oji\" />"},{"pid":"a981dde44b5515c37b730bad4fb1962f4c88b4cf","tid":237931,"uid":70505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T23:04:48.000Z","msg":"大陸仔返大陸啦，香港無人打撲嫁，屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"754ba3f3783a83c3e323ab122385a5b0c360cf55","tid":237931,"uid":22737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T23:09:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c4a025632cc1fcdf6f0a13fddfc6f31d5bd9f785","tid":237931,"uid":28401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T23:24:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fed8fc58997fd800f07e532e1ce4dbd668ed5132","tid":237931,"uid":5866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T23:25:42.000Z","msg":"沒有誰比誰高尚/更值得存在<br />\n價值觀同你唔同=起底？<br />\n噉應該起埋你底/起你底先<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?feature=youtu.be&amp;v=SreSDUCCW30\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ffeature%3Dyoutu.be%26v%3DSreSDUCCW30&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=3de2cce1\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?feature=youtu.be&amp;v=SreSDUCCW30</a><br />\n<br />\n「禽獸」可說是一首關於咒罵別人的歌，歌曲段落分不同視點出發，<span style=\"color: red;\">首段是第一個角色﹝小人﹞去道出所有缺德的東西，如「沒有公德心，沒有秀色可餐便等於饑饉&hellip;&hellip;沒有羞恥心、開口要講金、說沒有迷人銅臭會敢恥笑窮人難發奮&hellip;&hellip;」這一段表現出個人的一種價值觀。</span><br />\n<br />\n第二段是另一角色<span style=\"color: gold;\">﹝偽君子﹞大罵他痛狠的那個小人，罵人的行為其實與所謂的小人無異。指責一個標籤性的禽獸有錯很容易，亦令人安心。內容同樣不堪入耳。故事慢慢伸延到兩人反思，小人口沒遮欄的行為看似衰格低莊，但內心有時羨慕偽君子自恃有高尚情操感覺良好就暢所欲言，以歪理當正理去演講。這是偽君子無敵的地方。反而小人完全不懂動聽地於世演繹歪理。</span><span style=\"color: red;\">禽獸一般解作無恥無德之徒，而禽獸這個人沒有秘密有所隱瞞，這才是崇高的情操。</span><br />\n<br />\n歌詞精選<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你這嘴巴要給獸醫開刀</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">但我痛恨你便去咒罵你快落到地獄時辰就到<br />\n亦教壞細路 和你同路</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">偽君子悶得冤枉 不屑真小人無恥得夠放</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">見話兒便講有話兒便講</span> <span style=\"color: gold;\">我用人話去罵人或比你更骯髒</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">禁忌全曝光製造歧視爽</span> <span style=\"color: gold;\">我亦歧視粗鄙的你咒詛你很爽</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">禽獸來揭露 人性從未 崇高<br />\n誰博誰叫好 聲討老粗<br />\n暗裏羨慕</span>"},{"pid":"10647c630cad0107c6ec5f9574235769fd45b7f9","tid":237931,"uid":34473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T23:29:12.000Z","msg":"本身見到標題諗住入嚟撲你老母<br />\n<br />\n見你咁有point，正評左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再撲你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係仆唔係撲呀仆街仔"},{"pid":"d6c36cd1507c0d414d0cc889faa64186156002fb","tid":237931,"uid":3095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T23:38:06.000Z","msg":"ok網絡公審<br />\n傻西都有百幾正評"},{"pid":"719332e2940c954d657adaf0bf2093a072179847","tid":237931,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T23:39:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩叫撲街🤔🤔🤔</blockquote><br />\n大陸狗講法"},{"pid":"35f83fb528f59ed966c36547b9c8dc586f4cec04","tid":237931,"uid":52911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T23:39:26.000Z","msg":"呢個post勁多今次炒車既傻鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dccfc7d2a11cf3b8f6090ebbf953301ef3fa4c21","tid":237931,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T23:40:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大陸狗收皮啦 字都未識打<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"1c3e12f1f5fd41c64b1c642e24bcf88c43274b09","tid":237931,"uid":69168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T23:41:02.000Z","msg":"屌，口德-50分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac355553759de7f2546dbfa331297b138e3d466f","tid":237931,"uid":16384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T23:58:34.000Z"